Comparison diagram: Three Multi-Agent Architecture Patterns. 1) SUPERVISOR-WORKER: User -> Supervisor -> [Worker A: Research, Worker B: Analysis, Worker C: Report] -> Supervisor aggregates -> Answer. 2) PIPELINE: User -> Agent A: Extraction -> Agent B: Analysis -> Agent C: Generation. 3) DEBATE: Agent A: Pro + Agent B: Contra -> Mediator -> Synthesis. Three distinct flow diagrams side by side, German labels.